comments: Gordon (ORL) makes slight contact with Randle (NYK) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Bullock (NYK) briefly engages with Ross (ORL) during the screen.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Randle's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact.
Payton (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Ross (ORL) makes marginal contact to Randle's (NYK) side at the end of his drive.
Gordon (ORL) lightly brushes Randle's (NYK) arm during his shot attempt.
Bullock (NYK) places his hand against Ross' (ORL) back on the perimeter and removes it at the start of his upward shooting motion.
Fultz (ORL) maintains legal position as he moves alongside of Payton (NYK) during his drive.
Gibson (NYK) briefly engage and disengage with Vucevic (ORL) during the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes legal position in Payton's (NYK) path during the pick and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Payton (NYK) makes contact to Fultz's (ORL) body that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Fournier's (ORL) during the screen.
Gordon (ORL) briefly places his arm to Randle's (NYK) front during his drive to the basket.
Payton (NYK) and Carter-Williams (ORL) make marginal contact with one another during the rebound.
The referee crew fails to recognize the verbal and visual signal of Coach Clifford (ORL) attempting to call a timeout prior to the turnover.
Payton (NYK) extends his leg and makes foot to foot contact with Fournier (ORL) that affects his SQBR.
Gibson (NYK) makes incidental contact with Fournier (ORL) as is going to the ground.
Randle (NYK) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fournier (ORL) at the end of his drive.
